{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"c215ad32-e7f3-4654-9932-2da04d5a637e","content":"With **MSTest.Sdk/3.8.0**, Microsoft.Testing.Platform is actually the **default** runner. You only need to:\n\n1. **Remove** (or set to `false`) the `<UseVSTest>` property in your project file:\n\n```xml\n<!-- Remove this line -->\n<UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>\n```\n\n2. **Update CI/scripts** — the CLI output format changes slightly. `dotnet test` still works, but you can also run tests directly via `dotnet run`. Some VSTest-specific switches (e.g., `--logger trx`) become `--report-trx` instead.\n\n3. **Replace any VSTest-specific adapters/runsettings** — if you use a `.runsettings` file, pass it with `--settings`. Some VSTest logger arguments need updating to the new platform equivalents.\n\n**Key differences to watch for:**\n| VSTest | Microsoft.Testing.Platform |\n|---|---|\n| `--logger \"trx\"` | `--report-trx` |\n| `--filter \"Name=Foo\"` | `--filter \"Name=Foo\"` (same) |\n| `-- RunConfiguration.X` | `--settings file.runsettings` |\n\nNo package changes are needed — **MSTest.Sdk** bundles everything automatically.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"0dd312bd-3241-49de-9f30-952a3cafb5c4","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about migrating from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform in their MSTest project. This is a knowledge question about .NET testing configuration. Let me provide a concise answer based on my knowledge.\n\nWhen using MSTest.Sdk, switching from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform involves a few key changes:\n\n1. Remove or set `<UseVSTest>false</UseVSTest>` (or just remove it, since Microsoft.Testing.Platform is the default in newer MSTest.Sdk versions)\n2. Update how you run tests (use `dotnet test` or `dotnet run` depending on the version)\n\n\n3. Keep in mind there are some command-line differences between the two platforms that might affect how you invoke tests or pass arguments.","outputTokens":488,"requestId":"5C25:19AB05:A9A17:D2B51:69F54AEA"},"id":"92038173-c049-48be-8ccd-2ad8e797b7c8","timestamp":"2026-05-02T00:53:11.186Z","parentId":"27478153-f532-49a7-85d3-4601d6944b7a"}
